{"id": "art-19", "label": "Art. 19", "title": "Art. 19", "slug": "art-19", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1414887524\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1365\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1414887524\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 19 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_229446501\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1364\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_229446501\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În situa&#355;ia în care angajatorul nu informeaz&#259;\nsalariatul cu privire la toate elementele prev&#259;zute de prezenta lege,\nacesta poate sesiza Inspec&#355;ia Muncii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_285817961\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1363\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_285817961\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În cazul angajatorilor care au stabilite prin lege\norgane de inspec&#355;ie proprii, salariatul se adreseaz&#259; acestora.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1873992402\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1362\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image001.png\" o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20Muncii.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1873992402\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În situa&#355;ia în care angajatorul nu î&#351;i\nîndepline&#351;te obliga&#355;ia de informare prev&#259;zut&#259; la art. 17,\n18, 105 &#351;i 242, persoana selectat&#259; în vederea angaj&#259;rii ori\nsalariatul, dup&#259; caz, are dreptul s&#259; sesizeze instan&#355;a de\njudecat&#259; competent&#259; &#351;i s&#259; solicite desp&#259;gubiri\ncorespunz&#259;toare prejudiciului pe care l-a suferit ca urmare a\nneîndeplinirii de c&#259;tre angajator a obliga&#355;iei de informare.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}